{"tid":395422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同支那思想嘅老豆真係相處唔到","createTime":"2017-09-10T18:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T11:46:38.000Z","uid":96303,"like":52,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e70b0d33962d9d095fdee9b4d5e507a67c23704","tid":395422,"uid":96303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:16:55.000Z","msg":"因為屋企電腦喺廳<br />\n老母叫我熄機<br />\n佢諗住郁手打我<br />\n我就起身一野撞到佢仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(明明冇用力)<br />\n然後老豆就屌我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :老豆<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我<br />\n(嘈左一輪)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你咁勁就搵多啲錢黎寸我(佢比大部分連登仔搵少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我又唔係要同人比較，點解要寸人，你最鐘意同人比較嫁啦(同支那人晒錢行為有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :我幾時有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你叫細佬唔好成日學我咁打機嘛，明明直接講唔好打咁多機咪得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :同你講都哂氣，<span style=\"color: red;\">你地啲青年人最鐘意咪反，開心嘛，搞亂社會嘛</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :唔好將反同開心拉埋一齊講，明明兩個字冇直接意思，好似明明中華民國建立先，然後共產黨反佢然後建立中国，共產黨果時係開心先?(講到好似恭喜劉生事件咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :你知唔知國民黨果時有幾腐敗&hellip;(之後一輪講好多野，若蓮喪子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :所以我咪話唔好將反依個字醜化，拉埋好威好開心黎講<br />\n<br />\n然後佢突然郁手打我(支那人講唔啱數就郁手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )好彩我反應快避開即還手推開佢黎對坑(香港人，唔係比人踩到上心口都唔反掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n <br />\n最後細佬同老母出黎阻止<br />\n佢仲係咁話我心胸狹窄<br />\n遲啲分分鐘連家用都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你唔又反省下點解我只係同你搞到咁僵<br />\n冇學識又要講到自己乜撚野都啱晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真我真係唔撚識同你相處<br />\n如果我唔係學生我早就搬左出去住啦<br />\n洗撚靠你咩自量下啦"},{"pid":"f6992c370b362269238ce182f80490e07392f2b3","tid":395422,"uid":74262,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:20:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf41b137dfea6143b3264f47344d44a320e686f5","tid":395422,"uid":96303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由你一同佢講野個刻開始你已經on9左</blockquote><br />\n我個人比較衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24982aa2908b23d63a769fdfc64ef677c7072130","tid":395422,"uid":126902,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T18:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>由你一同佢講野個刻開始你已經on9左</blockquote><br />\n我個人比較衝動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對呢挺人quote中共啲嘢佢咪駁唔到<br />\n等同對住偽善嘅耶撚句句quote聖經一樣<br />\n我試過無端端講<br />\n我呢生人最敬重毛主席一樣嘢<br />\n就係多謝日本侵略中國<br />\n被街邊啲阿叔屌鑊甘"},{"pid":"2aa6db8a40b3a4bd700790e3988ce1c5969fe197","tid":395422,"uid":69021,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T21:12:40.000Z","msg":"唔洗同佢嘈<br />\n忍多幾年<br />\n佢咁巴閉，你依家就用曬佢d錢<br />\n第日你做左野，唔洗睇佢面色，就如佢所願，唔好比家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f8b1c12c2c7ee1816dce3e68c355cf8e2190ca","tid":395422,"uid":64131,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T23:09:57.000Z","msg":"你懶係講道理其實1999好難頂"},{"pid":"68a3b422881ae18134f44f7256e29734dc172595","tid":395422,"uid":96303,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:10:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你懶係講道理其實1999好難頂</blockquote><br />\n其實我一開始認左我衝動唔小心整親老母<br />\n佢仲要拉埋其他野黎閙<br />\n係咁講你冇人性<br />\n唔講道理唔通郁鳩佢咩"},{"pid":"be98c5d5d56dfb0a0990c8e3b9f65846c203e462","tid":395422,"uid":59641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T00:18:35.000Z","msg":"記得真係唔好俾家用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9a71c67de81c7f85cf9e552fa34d4bf142f8ac","tid":395422,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:01:58.000Z","msg":"講野佢又點, 改變唔到現實<br />\n<br />\n最實際係搬走, 唔比家用由佢自生自滅."},{"pid":"1a2f1021bf48a63de91896a580a0098509ac6c52","tid":395422,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T01:02:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講贏佢又點, 改變唔到現實<br />\n<br />\n最實際係搬走, 唔比家用由佢自生自滅.</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d7138e728d39300f5988115636c75c31acf34fd7","tid":395422,"uid":57308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"1999"},{"pid":"c16103f6270e33773df0874dd2b455fdcee521e8","tid":395422,"uid":24217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:04:16.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"497b5fd4d3bd401e67cf7eb79a5569086fd3c266","tid":395422,"uid":62650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T20:17:51.000Z","msg":"我屋企人都係咁。講到D學生好似社會敗類咁。又唔諗下點解佢地背後。真係到時有事真係唔好怪人"},{"pid":"13c353ea8d73ba84fdbfb75b848cae60d307a2cc","tid":395422,"uid":80805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我屋企人都係咁。講到D學生好似社會敗類咁。又唔諗下點解佢地背後。真係到時有事真係唔好怪人</blockquote><br />\n岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係日日聽奶共對話真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfac5531b89c9c31ed96742f8ed8df68810841df","tid":395422,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T11:17:28.000Z","msg":"仆：渣ga"},{"pid":"8fdf48e1ee407ed9918d666ba6f7a82d1cbb4b65","tid":395422,